of the age, hmm?

519
00:37:08,159 --> 00:37:09,160
Hmm?

520
00:37:11,696 --> 00:37:12,936
Simpson.

521
00:37:13,564 --> 00:37:15,202
Any thoughts?

522
00:37:15,266 --> 00:37:17,212
