524
00:37:20,371 --> 00:37:23,875
But might you perhaps
care to elaborate?

525
00:37:25,476 --> 00:37:27,854
- There was great unrest, sir.
- (students laugh)

526
00:37:31,082 --> 00:37:32,561
Oh, dear.

527
00:37:32,617 --> 00:37:34,187
Anyone?

528
00:37:40,057 --> 00:37:41,058
Finn?

529
00:37:41,125 --> 00:37:44,129
Now, I'm conscious
it's your first day with us,

530
00:37:44,195 --> 00:37:48,234
but, um, any thoughts?

531
00:37:51,335 --> 00:37:53,713
