what I don't know, sir,

533
00:37:55,706 --> 00:37:58,846
that's philosophically self-evident.

534
00:37:59,710 --> 00:38:03,783
What we do know is that
something happened, sir.

535
00:38:03,848 --> 00:38:05,020
Professor:
Come again?

536
00:38:05,082 --> 00:38:08,086
Well, something happened.

537
00:38:08,152 --> 00:38:12,692
All one can ever truly say of
any particular period of history, sir,

538
00:38:12,757 --> 00:38:14,395
