543
00:38:24,168 --> 00:38:26,876
Well, I thought you made
an extremely valid point.

544
00:38:26,937 --> 00:38:28,848
I'm, uh, Tony Webster.

545
00:38:28,906 --> 00:38:30,214
I'm Adrian Finn.

546
00:38:37,982 --> 00:38:39,461
It's cheery.

547
00:38:39,517 --> 00:38:41,428
