with Dylan Thomas?

548
00:38:41,485 --> 00:38:43,089
Hmm, yes.

549
00:38:43,888 --> 00:38:47,131
I find him to be one of the most
humane poets of the 20th century.

550
00:38:47,191 --> 00:38:49,002
Boy: But then he did say it,
