Parents, what a load of effing bastards.

552
00:38:52,897 --> 00:38:56,367
Adrian Finn, Colin Simpson.
Colin Simpson, Adrian Finn.

553
00:38:56,434 --> 00:38:59,381
- Hello, Adrian Finn.
- And, uh, this is Alex Stuart.

554
00:38:59,437 --> 00:39:02,714
Oh, really great line to Hunt,
really great.

555
00:39:02,773 --> 00:39:04,051
Is there an issue
with your parents?

556
00:39:04,075 --> 00:39:06,112
Ugh, "issue" is putting it mildly.

557
00:39:06,177 --> 00:39:07,454
Just when you think
you can trust them...

558
00:39:07,478 --> 00:39:10,391
- Effing bastards.
- Just when you think you can trust them,

559
00:39:10,448 --> 00:39:12,257
