- notions of time.

565
00:39:24,895 --> 00:39:26,636
It also looks quite cool.

566
00:39:28,299 --> 00:39:31,143
Colin:
So, Dylan Thomas, interesting.

567
00:39:31,202 --> 00:39:32,272
Yes.

568
00:39:33,471 --> 00:39:35,542
- Any good?
- Do you know him?

569
00:39:35,606 --> 00:39:37,950
- Not really.
