Okay.

608
00:41:48,939 --> 00:41:51,579
We are told Dobson
came to take his own life,

609
00:41:51,642 --> 00:41:54,088
perhaps when he understood
his girlfriend was pregnant.

610
00:41:54,144 --> 00:41:56,021
